{"tid":876400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲學打Golf一齊交流下","createTime":"2018-10-25T14:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T02:44:42.000Z","uid":75432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2b3c08bd3b8256cf4bd390bc31e21f96e31427","tid":876400,"uid":75432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"細佬學左大半年 有落過場 有打斷過桿<br />\n平時係練習場都好少見到差唔多年紀既人練波咁<br />\n全部都係阿叔<br />\n<br />\n有打嘅想學嘅都黎交流下<br />\n講下點練<br />\n講下球桿<br />\n講下球場<br />\n講下球童都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b3611f93571694f3d13f76ef2c84224b18dedc","tid":876400,"uid":75432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T15:38:50.000Z","msg":"咁都有負評<br />\n講下我學打golf<br />\n最初都以為好貴<br />\n原來請個教練1對1咁教都係4舊水一粒鐘起錶 平過學琴<br />\n一開始買左十堂 即係十粒鐘 一個星期上一堂 <br />\n已經略有小成 其實只係可以將個波打起 個波會飛去邊就要再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時放工唔洗OT就去練習場練番一粒鐘 盛惠50蚊<br />\n打golf睇落好簡單 拎住支桿 一個轉身就打到個波飛去<br />\n教練都係咁講 原理都係果三篤屁<br />\n但到自己做呢就<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181002/large/e8809a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181002%2Flarge%2Fe8809a.jpg&h=7504e1ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ff243e8b44a69d510df83e6b2008cd9d5194e3e","tid":876400,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T20:38:54.000Z","msg":"6 歲開始打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去邊打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986ee3f66e1c3ff2bcc6c491932f8cc02a2cfa50","tid":876400,"uid":75432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ff243e8b44a69d510df83e6b2008cd9d5194e3e","tid":876400,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T20:38:54.000Z","msg":"6 歲開始打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去邊打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"未係香港落過場<br />\n番大陸打多"}]}